Package: peakPerformR
Title: Cross-Sport Analysis of Peak Performance Age Using Spline Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Analyzes player performance data across multiple sports to identify
    peak performance ages and career trajectories. The package provides tools to
    build, process, and visualize data from various sports leagues including MLB,
    NFL, NBA, NHL, MLS, PWHL, NWSL, WNBA, and chess.
